Sentencas: Interconnect layers on stainless steel substrates (STS430) for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC) were built up by atmospheric plasma spraying (APS) using spray dried La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF) and blended LSCF/Ag composites.
Titulo: Effects of Silver Addition on Properties and Performance of Plasma Sprayed La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ Interconnect Layer

Sentencas: The microstructure and phase of each coating were analyzed using scanning electron microscopy (SEM) and x-ray diffraction (XRD) studies, respectively.
Titulo: Effects of Silver Addition on Properties and Performance of Plasma Sprayed La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ Interconnect Layer

Sentencas: Furthermore, bond strength, microhardness, performance in a thermal cycle test and in an oxidation test, and electrical conductivity were measured and compared.
Titulo: Effects of Silver Addition on Properties and Performance of Plasma Sprayed La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ Interconnect Layer

Sentencas: The coatings prepared from spray dried LSCF have higher porosity and more cracks within the splats and at intersplat boundaries.
Titulo: Effects of Silver Addition on Properties and Performance of Plasma Sprayed La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ Interconnect Layer

Sentencas: In contrast, the coatings prepared from LSCF/Ag had fewer cracks and less porosity due to the relatively high ductility of silver.
Titulo: Effects of Silver Addition on Properties and Performance of Plasma Sprayed La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ Interconnect Layer

Sentencas: After oxidation testing at 800 degrees C for 200 h, the weight change of the STS430 substrate and the LSCF and LSCF/Ag-coated alloys were found to be 0.06833, 0.01950, and 0.01656 mg/cm(2), respectively.
Titulo: Effects of Silver Addition on Properties and Performance of Plasma Sprayed La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ Interconnect Layer

Sentencas: Also the electrical conductivity of LSCF and LSCF/Ag coatings were higher than that of STS430 by two orders.
Titulo: Effects of Silver Addition on Properties and Performance of Plasma Sprayed La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ Interconnect Layer
